@node HISTORY "History"

1.2 : 16.07.95
    - Added NOBACKDROPS option again... I lost the source to version 1.1
      due to a HD error :( This version is actually smaller than the previous!
      Thank god for the Junction 9 BBS!!!!

1.4 : 01.12.96
    - Project taken over by me, Juan J. García de Soria Lucena.
    - Added NUMBER, METHOD, STEPS, MAXPEN, CYCLE and RANDOM options.
    - Now there are 6 different animations.
    
1.5 : 18.12.96
	- Added NOBORDERLESS option. A lot of people complaint about CaBoom going
	  unusable with MagicMenu.
@endnode





